body.name: Hyomdeck Reversible L Shaped Gaming Desk with Power Outlets and USB Charging Ports, Sturdy Computer Desk with Storage Shelf, Modern Corner Desk Home Office Table, Easy to Assemble, Gray Oak
features: Flexible Design with 3 Different Configurations: There are three ways to put the computer desk together in different orientations. This computer table can be placed anywhere as you want. You can chose it to be a left or right corner desk for full use of corner space, or a long table for 2 people working together. The two desktop provide you ample room to take one side for computer monitors as work area and other side for gaming and writing area.

Functional Power Strip: The 3 power outlets and 2 USB charging ports on the desktop is a nice touch to help plug in the items that are moved around, such as laptop charge, phone charger, tablet, gaming gear, printer etc, which bring you great convenience for daily use. You don’t have to bend over to look for wall socket.

Extra Storage Shelf and Space Saving: To save on space, the l shaped computer desk includes a storage shelf underneath to provide stability to legs and are very convenient to store headphones, routers, controllers, books and files etc. Saves from cluttering up the top of your desk. There are also a shelving spot to store a PC tower, which can be adjustable to meet your different needs.

Sturdy and Well-made: The l shaped office desk is made of engineered wood and heavy duty metal frame for strength and stability. The solid construction ensure the durability and lasting use. It features a sturdy desktop for holding your computers, monitors and printers. With clean and ergonomic design, it create a stylish and comfortable work area. Great addition to your home office.

Easy to Assemble and Versatile: This is the perfect size and fit well for corner area or small space without taking up your space. The light weight and compact design make it easy to move to anywhere you needed it. The instruction is super easy and straightforward, which is easy to follow all the options. This desk table can set up in the corner of your home office room, study room, living room, bedroom, gaming room, kid’s room, play room into a workstation, gaming area or writing area etc.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Get this roomy and sleek looking desk for work from home. This table can offer more spaces and you can take full advantage of desk space. This is a great functional computer desk that easily hold computers, printers, lots of papers and whatever else you would keep on a desk.
Extra Storage Space The shelves underneath is a nice touch to be able to put extra items, which is great for a laptop docking station. This leaves plenty of desk space open to work on.

It is configurable to 3 different ways. You can put in the corner as a left l shaped desk or right l shaped desk, or you can also put it as a two person long desk to meet your different needs. How versatile it is and it's so gorgeous.

Convenient Power Socket Upgrade the Look of Your Home Office or Workspace with Hyomdeck Aesthetically Pleasing and Functional L Shaped Desk. Perfect for someone who want to avoid a cluttered desktop since the workspace is limited. Roomy and Space Saving It fits monitor, scanner, printer and laptop easily and you still have work room for your cricut. Extra Storage Space the shelves underneath provide nice storage. This leaves plenty of desk space open to work on Convenient Power Socket It comes with attachable power outlets and USB charging ports which is extremely helpful for charging devices. Sturdy and Stable With thick board and solid construction, the desk is very sturdy. The adjustable leg pads make sure the stability of this table. Great Quality The desk is made from high-quality materials that are built to last. The desktop is also scratch resistant and easy to clean. Easy to Put Together Assembly instruction is clear, so it is pretty simple to set up and easy to move around. Color Options Gray Oak, Rustic Brown, Black, White
